9. Diffrence between Private VPC and Public VPC?
Public Subnet

Has route to Internet Gateway
Used for: Load balancer, bastion host

Private Subnet

No direct internet access
Uses NAT Gateway for outbound
Used for: EC2, RDS

10. you have a RDS database. So there is a concept called Multi-AZ. and there is a concept called Read Replicas. So what is the difference between these two?
Multi-AZ

Used for High Availability
Synchronous replication
Automatic failover
Same DB, standby instance

Read Replica

Used for Read Scaling
Asynchronous replication
No automatic failover (mostly manual)
Used to reduce read load

